  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"poisson\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-poisson\"></span>\n<h1>poisson<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#poisson\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">poisson</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">x</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></em>, \n         <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">name</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">|</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/tensor/random.py#L255\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Returns a tensor filled with random number from a Poisson Distribution.</p>\n<div class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\n           \\[out_i \\sim Poisson (lambda = x_i)\\]\n         </div>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>x</strong> (<em>Tensor</em>) – A tensor with rate parameter of poisson Distribution. The data type should be bfloat16, float16, float32, float64.</p></li>\n<li><p><strong>name</strong> (<em>str</em><em>|</em><em>None</em><em>, </em><em>optional</em>) – The default value is None. Normally there is no need for user to set this property. For more information, please refer to <span class=\"xref std std-ref\">api_guide_Name</span>.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">\n           Returns\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\">\n<p>Tensor, A Tensor filled with random number with the same shape and dtype as <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">x</span></code>.</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">\n<pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">paddle</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set_device</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'cpu'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">seed</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">uniform</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"nb\">min</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mf\">1.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"nb\">max</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mf\">5.0</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">out</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">poisson</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">out</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\n<span class=\"go\">Tensor(shape=[2, 3], dtype=float32, place=Place(cpu), stop_gradient=True,</span>\n<span class=\"go\">[[2., 5., 0.],</span>\n<span class=\"go\"> [5., 1., 3.]])</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>"
